Home Automation System

Author: Chris Horrocks
Email: ChrisjHorrocks@gmail.com

Language: Python
Platforms: *nix, RaspberryPi, Arduino

Description: A home automation app for controlling and scheduling temperature and lighting. Being built on the RaspberryPi dev platform using Arduino sheilds to interface with home electricals (Heaters, Fans, Lightswitches, etc).
